                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18250915-221-off1173 t18250915-221-cd1174"></join>, a pair of trousers, value 15 s.
            </rs> the goods of 
               <persName id="t18250915-221-victim1152" type="victimName">
                  Michael Henry 
                  Hart
               <interp inst="t18250915-221-victim1152" type="surname" value="Hart"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18250915-221-victim1152" type="given" value="Michael Henry"></interp>
